<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="sk">
  <head>
    <%- include('../templates/meta.ejs')-%>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/swiper/swiper-bundle.min.css" />
    <title>OSA Virtual Challenge</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header class="page-header bg-img__hard">
      <div class="l-page-container">
        <%- include('../templates/nav.ejs')-%>
        <div class="py-4 grid-columns-2">
          <section>
            <h1 class="page-header__headline">
              Balík - Hard
              <span class="headline-underline"></span>
            </h1>
            <p class="page-header__text">
              Tu sú len dve možnosti. Buď je to presne o Tebe, alebo to ešte len
              zistíš. Máš na to?
            </p>
            <ul class="challenge-meta">
              <li class="challenge-meta__item">
                <span class="fas fa-running fa-lg fa-fw mr-05"></span>
                <div class="challenge-meta__text challenge-meta__text--strong">
                  <span class="subheading">Kategórie</span><br />
                  Beh / Bicykel / Turistika
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="challenge-meta__item">
                <span class="fas fa-tag fa-lg fa-fw mr-05"></span>
                <div class="challenge-meta__text challenge-meta__text--strong">
                  <span class="subheading">Cena</span><br />
                  105 €
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="challenge-meta__item">
                <span class="fas fa-trophy fa-lg fa-fw mr-05"></span>
                <div class="challenge-meta__text challenge-meta__text--strong">
                  <span class="subheading">Počet aktivít</span><br />
                  18
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="challenge-meta__item">
                <span class="fas fa-running fa-lg fa-fw mr-05"></span>
                <div class="challenge-meta__text challenge-meta__text--strong">
                  <span class="subheading">Aktivity z Hard - Run</span><br />
                  7 km / 9 km / 12 km <br />
                  15 km / 17 km / 21 km
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="challenge-meta__item">
                <span class="fas fa-biking fa-lg fa-fw mr-05"></span>
                <div class="challenge-meta__text challenge-meta__text--strong">
                  <span class="subheading">Aktivity z Hard - Bike</span><br />
                  50 km / 60 km / 70 km <br />
                  80 km / 90 km / 100 km
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="challenge-meta__item">
                <span class="fas fa-hiking fa-lg fa-fw mr-05"></span>
                <div class="challenge-meta__text challenge-meta__text--strong">
                  <span class="subheading">Aktivity z Hard - Hike</span><br />
                  5 km / 10 km / 15 km <br />
                  20 km / 25 km / 30 km
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="challenge-meta__item">
                <span class="fas fa-hourglass-half fa-lg fa-fw mr-05"></span>
                <div class="challenge-meta__text challenge-meta__text--strong">
                  <span class="subheading">Čas na zvládnutie</span><br />
                  90 dní
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/objednavka/vyzva/15" class="button mt-1"
              >Zapojiť sa do výzvy</a
            >
          </section>
          <section class="gifts text-light">
            <div class="text-center">
              <!-- Slider main container -->
              <div class="swiper-container">
                <!-- Additional required wrapper -->
                <div class="swiper-wrapper">
                  <!-- Slides -->
                  <div class="swiper-slide">
                    <img
                      class="gifts__image"
                      src="https://res.cloudinary.com/osavirtual/image/upload/v1612457453/odmeny/RunHard_ti1abq.png"
                      alt="Medaila Hard-Run"
                    />
                  </div>
                  <div class="swiper-slide">
                    <img
                      class="gifts__image"
                      src="https://res.cloudinary.com/osavirtual/image/upload/v1612457453/odmeny/BikeHard_nyinbh.png"
                      alt="Medaila Hard-Bike"
                    />
                  </div>
                  <div class="swiper-slide">
                    <img
                      class="gifts__image"
                      src="https://res.cloudinary.com/osavirtual/image/upload/v1612457457/odmeny/HikeHard_taoi8u.png"
                      alt="Medaila Hard-Hike"
                    />
                  </div>
                  <div class="swiper-slide">
                    <img
                      class="gifts__image"
                      src="https://res.cloudinary.com/osavirtual/image/upload/v1612965544/odmeny/OSA_VirtualChallenge_Tricka_Run_ynqsku.png"
                      alt="Tričko OSA VIRTUAL CHALLENGE"
                    />
                  </div>
                  <div class="swiper-slide">
                    <img
                      class="gifts__image"
                      src="https://res.cloudinary.com/osavirtual/image/upload/v1612965545/odmeny/OSA_VirtualChallenge_Tricka_Bike_fx5pjw.png"
                      alt="Tričko OSA VIRTUAL CHALLENGE"
                    />
                  </div>
                  <div class="swiper-slide">
                    <img
                      class="gifts__image"
                      src="https://res.cloudinary.com/osavirtual/image/upload/v1612965545/odmeny/OSA_VirtualChallenge_Tricka_Hike_kmo7oc.png"
                      alt="Tričko OSA VIRTUAL CHALLENGE"
                    />
                  </div>
                  <div class="swiper-slide">
                    <img
                      class="gifts__image"
                      src="https://res.cloudinary.com/osavirtual/image/upload/t_gifts/v1613050193/odmeny/dres_ovch_p9ysj3.png"
                      alt="Cyklistický dres"
                    />
                  </div>
                </div>
                <!-- If we need pagination -->
                <div class="swiper-pagination"></div>

                <!-- If we need navigation buttons -->
                <div class="swiper-button-prev"></div>
                <div class="swiper-button-next"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <h2 class="gifts__title">Odmeny:</h2>
            <ul class="gifts__list fa-ul">
              <li class="gifts__item">
                <div class="gifts__highlight">
                  <span class="fa-li">
                    <span class="fas fa-check"></span>
                  </span>
                  10% zľava na štandardnom poplatku za jednotlivé výzvy
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="gifts__item">
                <div class="gifts__highlight">
                  <span class="fa-li">
                    <span class="fas fa-check"></span>
                  </span>
                  3 medaile v darčekovej pamätnej plakete
                </div>
                <div class="gifts__description">
                  v hodnote 40 € (medaile, balenie, poštovné)
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="gifts__item">
                <div class="gifts__highlight">
                  <span class="fa-li">
                    <span class="fas fa-check"></span>
                  </span>
                  Tričko s insígniami OSA VIRTUAL CHALLENGE
                </div>
                <div class="gifts__description">
                  v hodnote 10 € ... na výber varianta RUN, BIKE alebo HIKE
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="gifts__item">
                <div class="gifts__highlight">
                  <span class="fa-li">
                    <span class="fas fa-check"></span>
                  </span>
                  Darčeky s insígniami OSA VIRTUAL CHALLENGE 2021
                </div>
                <div class="gifts__description">
                  v cene 50 € ... Tričko alebo Bike dres alebo Batoh
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="gifts__item">
                <div class="gifts__highlight">
                  <span class="fa-li">
                    <span class="fas fa-check"></span>
                  </span>
                  20% zľava na ďalšie odevy z portfólia OSA VIRTUAL CHALLENGE
                  2021
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="gifts__item">
                <div class="gifts__highlight">
                  <span class="fa-li">
                    <span class="fas fa-check"></span>
                  </span>
                  Podporíš športový rozvoj detí v OSA Športovej akadémii
                </div>
                <div class="gifts__description">
                  v hodnote 2 € zo štartovného
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>
    <main>
      <section class="my-4">
        <div class="l-page-container">
          <h2 class="text-center">
            Informácie o výzve
            <span
              class="headline-underline headline-underline--centered"
            ></span>
          </h2>
          <p>
            Tri mesiace aktivít, tri mesiace plánovania, tri mesiace pohybu. To
            je 636 km aktivít, ktoré dajú zabrať! Budeš to práve Ty, kto sa ich
            odhodlá zdolať? My veríme, že sa nájde aspoň 10 statočných, čo túto
            výzvu pokoria. Tak sa pridaj a vydaj sa za zážitkami.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
      <%- include('../templates/rules.ejs')-%>
    </main>
    <%- include('../templates/footer.ejs') -%> <%-
    include('../templates/scripts.ejs') -%>
    <script type="module" src="/static/swiper/swiper-init.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
